44
00:06:45,794 --> 00:06:49,357
Only he can't tell an Alexandrine
from a decasyllabic verse

45
00:06:49,533 --> 00:06:51,934
Doinel, you'll conjugate
for tomorrow

46
00:06:52,103 --> 00:06:53,594
go to your seat

47
