53
00:07:30,064 --> 00:07:33,365
and erase those insanities, or I'll
make you lick the wall, my friend

54
00:07:37,376 --> 00:07:41,337
who gave you permission
to change seats, Richer?

55
00:07:51,532 --> 00:07:54,128
In the season when the thickets

56
00:07:58,777 --> 00:08:03,740
Glow with flowers

57
00:08:07,691 --> 00:08:10,218
When the black tip

58
00:08:20,946 --> 00:08:23,678
Of my long ears

59
00:08:24,852 --> 00:08:26,822
Could be seen

60
00:08:29,893 --> 00:08:31,760
Above

61
